        '\u003Cp\u003ELearn how to write a blog post that attracts and engages your target audience.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWe‚Äôve broken down the entire process. To help you achieve your content marketing goals and become a better writer.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELet‚Äôs get started.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E1. Choose a Blog Topic Idea\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFirst, decide what you‚Äôre going to write about.&nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe topic should be relevant to your brand. And interesting to your \u003Ca href="https://www.semrush.com/blog/target-audience/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"\u003Etarget audience\u003C/a\u003E.&nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIf you haven‚Äôt already, create \u003Ca href="https://www.semrush.com/blog/buyer-persona/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"\u003Ebuyer personas\u003C/a\u003E like the one below. To gain a better understanding of your target readers. And what type of content they‚Äôre interested in.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src="https://static.semrush.com/blog/uploads/media/6f/e7/6fe7927da31d4e7e5a603f67b3d7c36e/CHucSeQzdNE3qGiPWs52hpRh8joOPuYcr4UtWMUNtnyEJSmVxZwJiOnyTUIwGEppuLthUy6TgJXPatYGtx75_rQjXUSfzq4wfs42pQtLhFjvqjL9OZjftk1s4Vn1_OK8hvT1t2NvjA3dtLpqfxe6HZ0.jpeg" alt="A buyer persona created with Semrush Persona tool" height="1025" width="1010"\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThere are many ways you can come up with topics:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003ECheck out our list of \u003Ca href="https://www.semrush.com/blog/blog-ideas/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"\u003Eblog post ideas\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EConduct a \u003Ca href="https://www.semrush.com/blog/brainstorming/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"\u003Ebrainstorming\u003C/a\u003E session with your team\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003ELook at competing blogs for inspiration\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EAsk your audience what they want to read about (on social media or via email surveys)\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EPerform keyword research (step two explains how)\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFor a data-led approach to blog post ideation, try Semrush‚Äôs \u003Ca href="https://www.semrush.com/topic-research/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"\u003ETopic Research\u003C/a\u003E tool.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EClick ‚Äú\u003Cstrong\u003E+ Enter domain to find content on\u003C/strong\u003E.‚Äù\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src="https://static.semrush.com/blog/uploads/media/fc/c8/fcc85117ec10d0d16513393e0bde7d8c/qwgZcdMV0kYq9P1JdgHSppRu3vBJVpyU7o-_31okhP0_lQDhDyLVQzhZ8xSN7zEM-RlQEKVCrbGKCsNfVgF8RAmjUZxIWmOgR2oDIG_eGUCcTcN8CrZB_CIAvZIo2sebU04SBJPomL4BBFUFtK7xAKE.jpeg" alt="Topic Research tool" height="404" width="1010"\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEnter a broad topic idea. And your country and domain.&nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThen, click ‚Äú\u003Cstrong\u003EGet content ideas\u003C/strong\u003E.‚Äù\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src="https://static.semrush.com/blog/uploads/media/09/7e/097e0289631fe0079ab483d737f8ea99/DPnAhKND53n8WvSqy4_MYJfRmXo-v8PM_PP1GjmSCtXZLacOEs7Es9eFre4lwamFmvQdGKF187UPvrPLaAPNRqlon4LSIW8XTfL5oAY_eF74UGo2osU0XfOsX0ilA3EoiW0KB4Fe3EJeejX-FOXlalY.jpeg" alt="&quot;mountain bikes&quot; and example domain entered into Topic Research search bar" height="479" width="1010"\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe tool will provide a variety of content ideas.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThose marked green are already covered on your site. While those with a flame icon are trending.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src="https://static.semrush.com/blog/uploads/media/12/1c/121c38d31c6ef536e33186d0461b310f/YiVkBd7APHeWNrMLIecTgHD963b7xg5PFneXm8PTq-unE2oppxfzIrrVPLOTilSYlLDP3LwYDGXh-bI8_0fjD8h8ES1WfrcXav9X0W-onOQk6pwgMahaYXLfC0alIWN60gbb4U1kXUJ3lZXVzPTMq_I.jpeg" alt="Topic Research &quot;Content Ideas&quot; dashboard for &quot;mountain bikes&quot;" height="805" width="1010"\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EClick ‚Äú\u003Cstrong\u003EShow more\u003C/strong\u003E‚Äù on any subtopic to see:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESubtopic volume:\u003C/strong\u003E The \u003Ca href="https://www.semrush.com/blog/keyword-search-volume/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"\u003Esearch volume\u003C/a\u003E (average number of monthly searches) for the subtopic keyword\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDifficulty:\u003C/strong\u003E The subtopic‚Äôs \u003Ca href="https://www.semrush.com/blog/keyword-difficulty/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"\u003Ekeyword difficulty score\u003C/a\u003E, which measures how hard it is to rank highly for that keyword\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETopic Efficiency:\u003C/strong\u003E A measure of subtopic‚Äôs search volume relative to its difficulty (higher = better)\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHeadlines:\u003C/strong\u003E Headlines related to the subtopic (with links to the articles)\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EQuestions:\u003C/strong\u003E FAQs related to the subtopic\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERelated searches:\u003C/strong\u003E Queries from the ‚ÄúRelated searches‚Äù section in Google\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src="https://static.semrush.com/blog/uploads/media/8e/dd/8edd64c6380e0aedc7b7384de01e77f8/HBL47ivuc5hq3d1Vtdzs29S2L1dEWqkefrqepMye50fG-crlVPzLAEI3H2t44Te-sh7AQWMQn6Cimpmyinc5kHUXAZk0mw1l49wtNeO_bhydIvx4gbKAmRAKkJmO7X8Borz-KEMFnjs2sodWBxljAS0.jpeg" alt="&quot;Topic Efficiency&quot; &quot;Headlines&quot; and &quot;Questions&quot; sections highlighted in Topic Research dashboard" height="1012" width="1010"\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETo proceed with an idea, click ‚Äú\u003Cstrong\u003E...\u003C/strong\u003E‚Äù and choose one of the options.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src="https://static.semrush.com/blog/uploads/media/d0/0a/d00a9982529b2954646dfe9576ce2510/p29W-1Np6Wg-FjEcXE6z-yWEeV-hfYLayvdD8Gdopnp-cP2ROpMux9mWjskK-qKjNxGseDXWrHFvsOzFXCJlJx93krNNP9JtSmOCT6RyDp6GmOrfvs46p272ZEcb-g1oq-NrDaDe8zxo-TqXCTyreDg.jpeg" alt="‚Äú...‚Äù menu opened with &quot;Get ideas on this topic&quot; &quot; Send task to Trello&quot; &quot;Create SEO template&quot; and &quot;Dismiss this card&quot; options" height="876" width="1010"\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003ETip:\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cem\u003E For a more strategic approach to content production, create a \u003C/em\u003E\u003Ca href="https://www.semrush.com/blog/content-planning/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"\u003E\u003Cem\u003Econtent plan\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cem\u003E. This details all the content you‚Äôll create over the coming weeks or months. Including blog posts.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E',
